      narr:theme "V0 Scope: SMS Deep Link Demo" ;
      skos:broader narr:Milestones ;
      skos:note "V0 enables sending an SMS deep link that texts a number and loads an existing perspective share by ID. It uses a constrained read-only system prompt behind an auth boundary." .

